<HEADLINE>
<P>
METRO DIGEST / LOCAL NEWS IN BRIEF : MAN FATALLY STABBED IN ROOM AT HILTON 
HOTEL 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
The body of a 27-year-old man who had been fatally stabbed was found in his 
15th-floor room at the downtown Los Angeles Hilton hotel Friday afternoon, 
police said. 
</P>
<P>
The victim was identified as Kenneth Wayne Laws of Los Angeles. Hotel officials 
declined to say how long he had been staying at the hotel. 
</P>
</TEXT>
